propsSchema.description:
A date, time, or local datetime input that can optionally sync string values with canvas parameters. Values are stored without timezone conversion.

## Example

```json
{
  "type": "datetime-input",
  "props": {
    "label": "Start date",
    "param": "start_date",
    "mode": "date",
    "defaultValue": "2026-01-01"
  }
}
```
